post_text:
Pirate Steve's Crew Member forms are due by Tuesday, August 30th. If your child wants to participate please turn the form in with the $25 fee to the campus office or homeroom teacher. We are excited to be offering this mentoring program again and are looking forward to a new and exciting year!

And if you have not turned in the PTO membership form and the annual $10 donation you can send that to school with your child as well.

As always, thank you for supporting the Poth PTO!

post_text: Pirate Steve's Crew Members-This Friday, Nov. 6th, is the last home football game. Come out and support your first mates! Wear your crew member shirt to get in the game for free and participate in run out. If your first mate is a band member/color guard you get to hang out with them 1st quarter!
